Bobbie GUNDERSON, et vir, petitioners,
v.
INDIANA, et al. No. 18-462. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 19, 2019.

Motion of Minnesota Association of Realtors for leave to file a brief as amicus *1168curiae granted. Motion of Cato Institute, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Indiana denied.
